{
  "texts": [
    "This network consists of eight convolutional layers with 3 × 3 filters, progressively increasing in number from 64 to 512, inspired by VGGs architecture.",
    "To further enhance discrimination, we incorporate VGG-19 features and leverage Faster R-CNN (Girshick 2015) for object detection within the discriminator, enabling it to effectively differentiate between super-resolved and highresolution images.",
    "Faster R-CNN (Girshick 2015), developed by Microsoft as a two-stage object detector, has gained significant popularity for its effectiveness in analyzing satellite images.",
    "The model comprises of two interconnected subnetworks, namely the region proposal network (RPN) and the detector.",
    "The primary task of the RPN is to identify and extract region-specific characteristics associated with objects of interest."
  ]
}